def bs(val, l):
    i = 0
    j = len(l) - 1
    ans = -1
    while i <= j:
        mid = i + (j - i) // 2
        if l[mid] <= val:
            ans = mid
            i = mid + 1
        else:
            j = mid - 1
    return ans + 1

def bst(i, val):
    j = 100000000000
    ans = -1
    while i <= j:
        mid = i + (j - i) // 2
        if mid ** 2 > val:
            ans = mid
            j = mid - 1
        else:
            i = mid + 1
    return ans
